project.description: Get details of people whose age is 33
project.author: shiva28@javadeveloper.com

machineConfig.content:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<config xmlns="http://web-harvest.sourceforge.net/schema/1.0/config"
	scriptlang="groovy">


	<script><![CDATA[
		import java.util.ArrayList;
		list=new ArrayList();
	]]></script>

	<var-def name="data">
		<datastore name="peopledetails">
			select * from @this where age='33';
		</datastore>
	</var-def>

	<script><![CDATA[
		list =new ArrayList();
	]]></script>



	<loop item="rowdata">
		<list>
			<var name="data" />
		</list>
		<body>
			<script><![CDATA[
				map =new HashMap();
				map.put("firstname",rowdata.get("firstname"));
				map.put("lastname",rowdata.get("lastname"));
				map.put("age",rowdata.get("age"));
				list.add(map);
				println list;
			]]></script>

		</body>
	</loop>



	<export include-original-data="true">
		<multi-column list="${list}" split-results="true"> 
		<put-to-column-getter name="firstname" property="firstname"></put-to-column-getter> 
		<put-to-column-getter name="lastname" property="lastname"></put-to-column-getter> 
		<put-to-column-getter name="age" property="age"></put-to-column-getter> </multi-column> 
	</export>

</config>
